'''阿德拉屠杀'''是一次[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间的[[屠杀事件|屠杀事件]]，发生于[[2013年12月|2013年12月]]阿德拉镇的工业区，至少32名[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]、[[什叶派|什叶派]]、[[德鲁兹派|德鲁兹派]]和[[基督教|基督教]]教徒遇难。<ref name=barrel/>根据叙利亚政府和活动人士说法，这次屠杀是由恐怖組織[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]和附屬於「伊斯兰阵线」的武裝組織[[伊斯蘭軍|伊斯蘭軍]]制造的。<ref name=pottsmerc>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pottsmerc.com/general-news/20131213/syrian-troops-launch-offensive-after-dozens-killed |title=Syrian troops launch offensive after dozens killed |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073025/http://www.pottsmerc.com/general-news/20131213/syrian-troops-launch-offensive-after-dozens-killed |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 过程 ==
12月11日，根据目击者、活动人士和叙利亚国家电视台的报道，反对派武装伊斯兰阵线和[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]<ref name=alawiteanddruze>[http://in.reuters.com/article/2013/12/12/syria-crisis-adra-idINDEE9BB0AR20131212 Islamists kill 15 Alawite and Druze civilians in Syria -activists] {{Wayback|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2013/12/12/syria-crisis-adra-idINDEE9BB0AR20131212 |date=20151009172352 }} ''Reuters''. 12 December 2012.</ref>攻入大马士革东北阿德拉镇的工业区，攻击居住着工人及家属的房屋。反对派依据这些人的宗教派别进行杀戮，针对的是[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]、[[德鲁兹派|德鲁兹派]]、[[什叶派|什叶派]]和[[基督教徒|基督教徒]]。这些人当中有的被枪杀，还有的则被斩首。<ref name=pottsmerc/>这场杀戮持续到了第二天。<ref name=alawiteanddruze/>总计大约有19到40人<ref name=pottsmerc/><ref name=alawiteanddruze/>在反对派攻占阿德拉镇工业区后被杀害。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/173913/ |title=Many civilians feared dead as rebels capture town near Damascus |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225020121/http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/173913/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>还有18名亲政府民兵被杀，<ref name=expel>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/89044/World/Region/Syria-army-aims-to-expel-rebels-from-town-on-road-.aspx |title=Syria army aims to expel rebels from town on road to capital |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521043141/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/89044/World/Region/Syria-army-aims-to-expel-rebels-from-town-on-road-.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>其中有5名是巴勒斯坦解放军的成员。在反对派试图杀害一个什叶派家庭成员时，一名什叶派教徒引爆了身上的炸药，炸死了他本人及其家人以及多名反对派武装分子。<ref name=pottsmerc/>

12月3日，政府军包围了阿德拉镇，<ref name=pottsmerc/>开始采取行动将该地区的反对派武装赶出。<ref name=expel/>在当天政府军在该镇取得进展。<ref name=pottsmerc/>行动持续到了第二天。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-14/241107-syria-rebel-commander-freezes-to-death-monitor.ashx#axzz2nTHkoZHH |title=Syria rebel commander freezes to death: activists |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531092123/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-14/241107-syria-rebel-commander-freezes-to-death-monitor.ashx#axzz2nTHkoZHH |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

截止12月15日，总计有32名少数派人士在反对派对阿德拉的进攻中丧生，十余人失踪。<ref name=barrel>{{Cite web |url=http://www.news.com.au/world/syrian-regime-drops-barrel-bombs-in-air-attack-in-aleppo-78-dead-include-28-children/story-fndir2ev-1226783680713 |title=Syrian regime drops barrel bombs in air attack in Aleppo; 78 dead include 28 children |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030103033/http://www.news.com.au/world/syrian-regime-drops-barrel-bombs-in-air-attack-in-aleppo-78-dead-include-28-children/story-fndir2ev-1226783680713 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>叙利亚政府军宣称超过80人被伊斯兰武装分子杀害，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2013/12/16/Opposition-government-trade-accusations-of-slaughter-in-Syria/UPI-52361387200081/?spt=rln&or=2 |title=Opposition, government trade accusations of slaughter in Syria |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028015051/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2013/12/16/Opposition-government-trade-accusations-of-slaughter-in-Syria/UPI-52361387200081/?spt=rln&or=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而叙利亚外交部则声称超过100人被杀。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-12/17/c_125869068.htm |title=Al-Qaida militants kill over 100 Syrians near Damascus: FM |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2016-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018125900/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-12/17/c_125869068.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>俄罗斯记者报道叛乱武装挟持平民作为人盾，将包括儿童在内的居民活埋，还把一些人的头砍下挂在该镇一个广场的树上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anna-news.info/node/13127|title=Summary of events in Syria for 19 December|work=ANNA News|date=2013-12-21|accessdate=2013-12-21|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827212207/http://anna-news.info/node/13127|dead-url=no}}</ref>

12月30日，据报道叙政府军从阿德拉解救了大约5000人，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/syria-5000-evacuated-adra-955/ |title=Syrian govt evacuates 5,000 from town besieged by Islamist rebels |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190113232308/https://www.rt.com/news/syria-5000-evacuated-adra-955/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在31日，叙利亚政府新闻社报道更多的人被解救，使得被解救的人数超过6000人。<ref>[http://sana.sy/eng/21/2013/12/31/520266.htm More thousands of citizens evacuated from Adra into safe haven] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614032758/http://sana.sy/eng/21/2013/12/31/520266.htm |date=2014-06-14 }}</ref>

在2014年1月中旬，据报道重新控制了阿德拉镇并打通了通往该镇的[[补给线|补给线]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syria-geneva-ii-talks-scepticism-on-the-streets-asalqaida-poses-as-peacemaker-9084078.html |title=Syria Geneva II talks: Scepticism on the streets as al-Qa’ida poses as peacemaker |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925194342/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syria-geneva-ii-talks-scepticism-on-the-streets-asalqaida-poses-as-peacemaker-9084078.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

