{{flagicon|USA}} [[美国国务院|美国国务院]]指责了这起屠杀事件，并声称这是在阿德拉发生的最新的一起针对平民的屠杀事件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2013/218664.htm |title=Civilian Massacres in Syria |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114141412/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2013/218664.htm |archive-date=2014-01-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

